results.name: n-th row of the following triangle contains all distinct numbers that can be obtained as the product of three distinct numbers chosen from 1 to n (for n>2). Sequence contains the triangle read by rows.
reference: Amarnath Murthy, Generalization of partition function introducing Smarandache Factor Partitions, Smarandache Notions Journal, 1-2-3, Vol. 11, 2000.
xref: Numbers of terms in rows are given by A027430.
results.author: _Amarnath Murthy_ and Meenakshi Srikanth (menakan_s(AT)yahoo.com), May 05 2003
